title: Rebel  Moon  Rising
description:
Title: Rebel Moon Rising
Genre: FPS / action / sci-fi
Released: 22nd December 1996
Developer: Fenris Wolf
Publisher: GT Interactive
Description:
One small step for the moon, one giant shock for mankind! The Lunar Free State has declared independence from the Earth. For a rebel Lunar Militiaman like you, that means strategic combat against the military might of the United Nations on treacherous moonscapes and space stations. Lunar combat assignments include infiltration, search and destroy, defense and rescue missions. Variable level gravity and limited oxygen supply will challenge even the most experienced lunar militiaman.

How to play:
1) Run rebelmoonrising_setup.exe to install the game;
2) Launch the game using its main executable or shortcuts.

! Notice
Tested and working fine on Windows 7 x64 with latest updates installed.
